        "color": 4,
        "width": 640,
        "height": 460,
        "content": "## üìã WORKFLOW PROCESS OVERVIEW\n\nStep 1: üöÄ Manual Trigger / Schedule Trigger initiates the workflow\nStep 2: ‚öôÔ∏è Set Project Key defines the Jira project identifier for ticket filtering\nStep 3: üé´ Get All Tickets from the specified project created today\nStep 4: üì§ Split Out extracts individual ticket data including key, summary, and description\nStep 5: üîÑ Loop Tickets processes each ticket individually through batch splitting mechanism\nStep 6: üí¨ Get Comments from Ticket retrieves all comments and conversations for each ticket\nStep 7: üîó Merge combines ticket data with its associated comments for complete context\nStep 8: ü§ñ Ticket Summarizer (AI Agent) analyzes ticket information using OpenAI GPT-5 to generate:\n - Professional ticket summary combining all relevant information\n - Proposed solution with step-by-step explanations\nStep 9: üìä Set Output structures the AI analysis into standardized JSON format\nStep 10: üìà Aggregate collects all processed ticket summaries into a single dataset\nStep 11: üìù Format Body creates a readable email format with ticket links to Jira\nStep 12: üìß Send Ticket Summaries delivers the daily report via Gmail with subject \"Daily Ticket Summaries ‚Äì [Date]\""
